data.title: Jan Waters - Chesterfield, MO Real Estate Agent
data.meta_description: Find real estate agent & Realtor® Jan Waters in Chesterfield, MO on realtor.com®, your source for top rated real estate professionals.
data.text: Service Areas and Specialties Member of 'Team Waters', specializing in single family homes, condominiums, investment and foreclosure properties throughout the St. Louis metropolitan area with emphasis in West St. Louis County. Dedicated to helping our clients achieve their real estate goals, our objective is to delight every client with personalized care, professional guidance and efficient administrative services. Our years of experience combined with the vast resources available to us, will contribute to your complete satisfaction. Put us to work for you and see what a difference we can make. Professional Experience Member of St Louis Association of Realtors Member of Missouri Association of Realtors Member of National Association of Realtors Graduate of Realestate Institute - Coldwell Banker Gundaker Short Sale and Foreclosure Specialist Extensive continuing education regarding market trends and license law Professional Education and Designations My Education is in Marketing and Sales and I have over 30 Years of Sales, Marketing and Management Experience. Personal I am married and reside in Clarkson Valley with my husband, Bob Waters, who is also my business partner and our (2) Bichon Frises, Brie and Einstein. We enjoy cooking, dining and entertaining. We are involved with our Church, the Ronald McDonald House and Assistance League of St Louis. We strive for 'Excellence' when it comes to Customer Service and we live by the 'Golden Rule.' Afterall, 'Excellence Happens...Daily!'
